# Code Style

- Use ES modules (import/export), not CommonJS
- Use TypeScript with proper types - avoid `any` where possible
- Follow React hooks patterns and best practices
- Component library: PatternFly React (`@patternfly/react-core`, `@patternfly/react-table`)
- Use `@emotion/css` for styling when needed, avoid generating plain css/scss files
- Routing: `react-router-dom` with BrowserRouter
- Destructure imports when possible: `import { Button } from '@patternfly/react-core'`
